trans-unit.source: Provides a read-only collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona una colección de sólo lectura de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> class represents a read-only collection of objects, typically used by <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> objects to manage sets of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> clase representa una colección de solo lectura de objetos, normalmente <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> y <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> objetos para administrar conjuntos de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objetos.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control uses a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> collection to keep a list of available <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects on a page, whereas a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> object uses a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> collection to track the available <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects that it contains.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control utiliza un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> colección para mantener una lista de elementos disponibles <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objetos en una página, mientras que un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> de objeto usa un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> colección para realizar un seguimiento de los contadores <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objetos que contiene.

trans-unit.source: Although the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> collection is read-only, you can make programmatic changes to the properties of the underlying controls referenced in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Aunque el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> colección es de solo lectura, puede realizar cambios mediante programación a las propiedades de los controles subyacentes que se hace referencia en la colección.

trans-unit.target: Una colección de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" />.

trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection" /> que contiene los objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> especificados.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection.Contains%2A> method enables you to check a particular <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> object and determine whether it is part of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection.Contains%2A> método le permite comprobar un determinado <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objeto y determinar si forma parte de un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> colección.

trans-unit.target: Matriz de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> que va a contener la colección copiada.

trans-unit.source: The starting point in the array at which to place the collection contents.
trans-unit.target: Posición inicial de la matriz en la que se va a colocar el contenido de la colección.

trans-unit.target: Copia la colección en una matriz de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection.CopyTo%2A> method is useful when you want to assemble a custom array that can contain all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> collection, a subset of those objects, or a superset of those objects.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection.CopyTo%2A> método resulta útil cuando desea ensamblar una matriz personalizada que puede contener todos los <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objetos en el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> colección, un subconjunto de esos objetos o un superconjunto de los objetos.
